{"title":"月下怀想","authors":["宋道敏"],"dates":[{"year":1993,"month":6,"day":25}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"月下怀想"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宋道敏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"城市疏远季节"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日子是一沓整齐的台历"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这时，该又是母亲坐在院里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梳理苞米的时候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"银也似的月光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"辉映丝丝白发"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"酿成乡村特有的静谧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任凭月亮阴晴圆缺"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"属于泥土的双手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远没有闲暇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一生围着锅台转"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看守炉火不熄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是她永恒的职业"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"期待的目光里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放飞一群儿女远去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无数个艰辛染成了年逾古稀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今晚，默吟唐诗宋词"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我抚动溶溶月光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多么像母亲的银丝"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}